            ┌ Help — press ? or Esc to close ──────────────────────┐            
            │ Keyboard Shortcuts                                   │            
            │                                                      │            
            │  Tab        Move focus between scrollable boxes      │            
            │  ↑ / ↓     Scroll the focused box                    │            
            │  Home/End   Scroll top / bottom                      │            
            │  Space      Pause / resume translation               │            
            │  T          Toggle TTS audio output                  │            
            │  M          Toggle metrics panel (compact/expanded)  │            
            │  L          Change target language                   │            
            │  S          Settings (F2/Ctrl+D cycles devices)      │            
            │  R          Reload config from disk                  │            
            │  ?          Show / hide this help                    │            
            │  Esc        Dismiss this overlay                     │            
            │  q / Ctrl+C Quit — shows session summary             │            
            └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
